SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1532 as follows:
1. On Page 10, Line 18, by deleting after the word “deductions,” and before the word
“employment” the words “timekeeping and badge entrance information,” and inserting the words
“information regarding an employee’s parking spot, the door or doors an employee routinely uses for
entry or exit, the time an employee routinely enters or exits the building”;
2. On Page 10, Line 24, by inserting after the period the words “Requests for the number of hours
worked shall be satisfied solely by providing timecard entry and exit information.”; and
3. By amending the title to conform.
Submitted by:
